{"tid":558411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚所有想戒煙既手足-戒煙日記","createTime":"2018-02-12T09:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T05:17:08.000Z","uid":124760,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"44953b800c21312d846703d4013dd7f800c7ed4d","tid":558411,"uid":124760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:02:58.000Z","msg":"戒過好多次都失敗，試過戒到無哂煙癮，但情緒排解唔到又食番。<br />\n所以最難既係心癮大過煙癮。<br />\n今次真係唔想再食，唔想比一樣野控制住。<br />\n一個戒癮既故事，每日一記。<br />\n喂！你連對人既心癮都戒到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，煙點會唔得呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33a5a444eb7ee07eb97a15846b61b15c0e12641","tid":558411,"uid":27289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:08:35.000Z","msg":"戒幾個月 食返<br />\n戒幾個月 食返<br />\n一有野煩就籍口多多"},{"pid":"6dfbdcf58019278cd34a95e999e048e123f912f8","tid":558411,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a33a5a444eb7ee07eb97a15846b61b15c0e12641","tid":558411,"uid":27289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:08:35.000Z","msg":"戒幾個月 食返<br />\n戒幾個月 食返<br />\n一有野煩就籍口多多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"Sad but true"},{"pid":"4b733d728b53000d47fc6fe13681c0766030746b","tid":558411,"uid":148511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:09:20.000Z","msg":"轉vape吧 <br />\n我做過最好既決定"},{"pid":"12f100cf4efa7d9432e73bf02f011d5fd0afd253","tid":558411,"uid":49457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b733d728b53000d47fc6fe13681c0766030746b","tid":558411,"uid":148511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:09:20.000Z","msg":"轉vape吧 <br />\n我做過最好既決定"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:00:10.000Z","msg":"呢隻食落咩味道?<br />\n我見街上d 人食噴好多煙出黎"},{"pid":"ac55ac5cb8cd0dc6b8991811d3a3d6794e79c046","tid":558411,"uid":156682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:10:34.000Z","msg":"支持你！<br />\n利申 絲打，好憎人食煙！如果你戒左，我肯